PROVENANCE

This package consolidates previously-separate sources:

1. TRUGS-DEVELOPMENT/TRUGS_TOOLS_development/ (private Xepayac/TRUGS-DEVELOPMENT mono-repo folder)
   — language-core CLIs, branch schemas, templates

2. TRUGS-LLC/TRUGS/tools/ (migrated in the `trugs` 2.0.0 breaking release)
   — TRL compiler, compliance_check, validate, graph-node CRUD (tget/tupdate/tdelete/tunlink)

As of 2.0.0 this package ships the language CLI `trug` only. Folder
cartography lives in the sibling `trugs-folder` package (`trug-a-folder`).

See TRUGS-LLC/TRUGS-DEVELOPMENT#1576 for the portfolio reorganization EPIC.
